  "ciliary_role": "Required for ciliogenesis. It might mark vesicles en route to the base of cilium, which is known to be crucial for ciliary assembly. Mutations cause JBTS (22282472). Mutated in OFD6 (26982032) and in Meckel syndrome MKS (21493627). Mutations or knockdown result in impaired ciliogenesis and centrosome docking. Modulates hyper- responsiveness of sig ling pathways mediated by Dvl and RhoA, suggesting they might be part of a complex to mediate cellular polarization and centrosomal apical docking (20512146).",
